Are you a local artist or craftsperson?
Wilson HS art students are asking artists to consider donating one of their works to the upcoming Empty Bowls fundraiser. All proceeds will benefit the Wilson Community Food Pantry. This is a great alternative to traditional basket auctions, and a terrific way for local artists to connect with the community and our students.
Please visit the Empty Bowls website (https://wcscares.weebly.com/art-donations.html) for more information. Tickets are also now on sale for $10 each. The Empty Bowls fundraising dinner will be held on March 25th from 5-7 PM.
